title: mRCC 5012
characteristics_ch1.2: disease status: Metastatic renal cell carcinoma (mRCC)

data_processing.1: Mapped miRNA profiles were normalized to RPM (read per million mappable count)
data_processing.2: 332 common miRNAs with >8 RPMs were choosed, normalized to RPM and performed log2 calculation
data_processing.4: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: tab-delimited text file include RPM values after log2  for each Sample
